# 🍴 Restaurant Management System (Console-Based Java Project)

A console-based restaurant order management app built in Java for handling menu items, orders, and billing with daily sales tracking.

## 🧩 Features
- Display and manage menu items
- Place and process multiple orders
- Apply discount codes
- Generate customer bills
- View daily sales reports

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- Java (Core + Collections)
- Console-based UI

## ▶️ How to Run
```bash
javac restaurant/Main.java
java restaurant.Main
